Exercise 1: 
Create a simple "div" with id "box". Add some Text content & set background color to "blue".

Exercise 2:
Create 3 headings of h1,h2 & h3. Give them all class "headings" & set color of "headings" to "red".

Exercise 3:
Create Button & set its background color:
    a) green using css stylesheet
    b) blue using <style> tag
    c) pink using inline style